Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Demon, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as ﻿Toon World remains on the field, I can't damage him in any of my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.01,0:01:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can't defend myself either...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there any way I can win in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You cannot possibly defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I give up now, all three of\N﻿their souls will he lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if my chances of victory \Nare low, I still can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is no use, Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how hard you struggle,\N you are still finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Counterattack Begins!\N The Mind Shuffle"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Also...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Magical Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By using the Black Magician in combo with the Silk Hats, I may be able to stop Pegasus from reading my attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm sure you plan to use this to stall time to\N﻿find out a way to stop my Toon World...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But I am afraid that is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your conscious will tell me which Silk Hat you hid Black Magician in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So that means by {\i1}you{\i0} knowing, I am {\i1}also{\i0} able to learn which hat he is hiding under.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm going to guess that you hid the Black Magician under the Silk Hat to the very left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it...! He read through me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you prepared, Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not even the\N Silk Hat combo works against him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't find a way to defeat\N the power Pegasus' Millennium Eye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi, don't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack one of the Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician has been reduced to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician's data didn't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The card is still on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me that I somehow managed to {\i1}miss{\i0} the Black Magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible... I should have read Yugi boys mind perfectly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to hide the location of the Silk Hat Black Magician is hiding in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...using {\i1}my{\i0} subconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like you couldn't read the other mind, {\i0}my{\i1} mind, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Another mind of Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Anzu... what does he\N mean by "another mind"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A seperate... mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Not long ago, Yugi told me himself he had another person inside himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What do you mean by that, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you guys, but the me that Duels isn't the usual me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always resting in my heart.\N I change to my Other Self to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just watch from within my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But in this Duel, I couldn't just stay hidden\N﻿and watch as my other self suffers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the\N Silk Hat combo works against him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find a way to defeat\N the power Pegasus' Millennium Eye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please! Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice just now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice came from within my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... other self!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You finally heard my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's the first time we were able meet in\N﻿our hearts. I can finally speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Until now, my voice never reached you,\N﻿no matter how loud I screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I could feel it when you were hurt in battle but I couldn't do anything to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But if finally reached!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please! Let me fight too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You can't handle Pegasus' power by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But... there's no way to fight against\N﻿the power of his Millennium Eye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus is able to read your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But... maybe he can't read mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's it! If Pegasus can only read one mind at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Maybe if we fight him with two minds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Will you lend me your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may find it hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Since I solved the puzzle, me and my other\N﻿self have been taking turns at living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, sometimes I feel like\NI have another me inside myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Yugi is Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This "other Yugi" he was talking about wasn't\N﻿just his imagination, but it actually exists...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple personalities switching places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Uh, is that what they call....\N uhh... split personalities, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll play this card face-down on the board and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus, do you know what the card I just drew and played face-down on the board is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try reading my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know once you do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Scan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There's no image of the set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry. but... I don't know what that set card is either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Reading my mind is pointless, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His mind just switched again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus, it seems to take you quite a large amount of time to read the opponent's mind with your Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switched minds while you were busy trying to read me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The way to beat your Millennium Eye is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Mind Shuffle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mind Shuffle...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's it! Yugi's using\N two minds to fight against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Even if Pegasus reads one of them, he can\N﻿just switch minds so the other can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright! He can do it! He can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You bastards! You no longer have anywhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's play a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If your weapons are those steel guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿...my weapon will be these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What kind of bullshit are you going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just give yourselves in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've seen this expression before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That time, it was the other Bakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That wasn't just a dream...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Man-Eater Bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He made something appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And with that, your turn has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There's no Duel System around here, and yet they're materializing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Then next is my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you mortals from the Man-Eater Bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although... Your situation {\i1}now{\i0}\N may be even {\i1}worse{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Th-this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now then, it's your turn, Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The Black Magician's location in the hats... even that set card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For it all to be concealed\N by the other Yugi boy's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿As long as Toon World remains on my side of the field, your Monsters cannot attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Magician can only hide in the silk hats for three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus, then pick the correct Silk Hat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿and annihilate the Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Or are you just a coward\N who can't trust your own ﻿intuition unless you\N rely on your Millennium Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, it has been several years since I relied upon my own instincts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No! I missed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What a pity. You've missed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus, since you're the creator of Duel\N﻿Monsters, l'm sure you're aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Every game has to\N have a winner and a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... What do you suppose seperates the two from one another?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}good judgment{\i0} needed to know the rules and assess the situation of the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And the {\i1}instincts{\i0}\N to decide when and how to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Whoever has these two things is the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Judgment comes from experience and confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Instinct requires divine courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But you've relied on the Millennium Eye's power for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And you've lost the instincts of a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to true courage, my partner is {\i1}far superior{\i0} to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿They switched minds again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a card I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll place this card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't see the idenity\N of those two set cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what these two set cards are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... I believe in the cards my other self played!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My card is Magic Neutralizing Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I will activate this card's effect on your side of the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This card wipes out the magic effects of every\N﻿card on the opponent's side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In other words, the magical effects of your Silk Hats will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dammit! Black Magician has been exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿And this is "the end", Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}﻿Skilled Duelists{\i0} don't {\i1}need{\i0} instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿They use their brains to strategize,\N﻿and to avoid taking risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Come forth, Toon Demon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only a Toon can defeat a Toon Monster..!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toon Demon will destroy the Black Magician with that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Toon Demon! Attack Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Set card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Effects Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What?! The Magic Effect Arrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus, you didn't notice, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿While I was drawing cards, the other me was trying to stall you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you got frustrated, you tried to play a card ﻿that would take out the effect of Magical Silk Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But that was what we were aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all magical effects sent {\i1}our way{\i0} are sent to {\i1}you{\i0} at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Pegasus! We're using the Magic Effects Arrow to return ﻿the effects of Magic Neutralizing Force to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But you're too late! You can't stop\N﻿The Toon Demon's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Black Magician is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}other{\i0} card I set...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card, Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Trap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the magical attack passes through ﻿the barrier and takes out Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Toon Monsters return to their original forms and appear on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Unbelievable!\N My.... my beloved monsters have all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is a nightmare! A bad dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!! This cannot be reality!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All right! All the Toons were destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! It was your courage\N that defeated the Toons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think Yugi boy's two minds could overcome my Mind Scan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright! You did it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(322,416)}﻿Yugi...! If you combine your two hearts ﻿together, you can beat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can save your grandfather\N and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what the hell is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I remember, Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That wasn't just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You aren't Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're the other Bakura from deep within Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so {\i1}honored{\i0} that you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now hand over Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Like I'd hand him to {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking to become a sacrifice for the Power of Darkness as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of Darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Exactly what I would expect from\N﻿one chosen by the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It seems I was\N playing around {\i1}far{\i0} too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must now face you in this Duel\N with the power and respect you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yugi boy, from now on,\N this will be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a fight between two people chosen by the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's settle this in a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Dark Game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked in the darkness, Yugi and Pegasus continue their battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So this is a Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't believe it, but this isn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just what is happening inside this giant sphere of darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We can feel Yugi's in great pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But there's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Next time!
